# Deps

[![Tests](https://github.com/apoclyps/deps/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/apoclyps/deps/actions/workflows/test.yml)
![pypi](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/deps.svg)
